  {
    "id": "1919033710890152148",
    "text": "We're living in an AI world, and sometimes I have to pinch myself:\n\n1. I still can’t believe you can write some English and software POPS out.\n\n2. I still can’t believe you can write some English and mobile app designs beautifully APPEAR\n\n3. I still can’t believe you can write some English and entire marketing campaigns MATERIALIZE.\n\n4. I still can’t believe you can write some English and financial models BUILD themselves.\n\n5. I still can’t believe you can write some English and personalized cold emails SEND themselves.\n\n6. I still can’t believe you can write some English and data visualization dashboards SELF-generate.\n\n7. I still can’t believe you can write some English and videos EDIT themselves into perfect clips.\n\n8. I still can’t believe you can write some English and millions of people can SEE what you wrote \n\n9. I still can’t believe you can write some English and business plans practically PITCH themselves.\n\n10. I still can't believe you can write some english and billions of people can come visit your store and BUY from it\n\n11. I still can’t believe you don’t even need to know English, you can just speak your language, and AI handles the rest. The world is YOUR oyster.\n\n12. I still can’t believe we’re this early\n\nAnd if you're reading this, congrats....\n\nYou're already ahead of 99% of people who haven't taken action yet.\n\nYou're lucky.",
